<p>INDIANAPOLIS (WTHR) â€” As more concerns arise about the coronavirus, Live Nation is putting a pause on its tours.</p>
<p>On March 12, <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/12/arts/music/coachella-concerts-coronavirus.html">the New York Times</a>
 reported that Live Nation will instruct "its touring shows to prepare 
